-MITCH: WELL,
THE TRADITION CONTINUES.

02:03.732 --> 02:05.951
FIRST NEELY, THEN DONNA.

02:06.082 --> 02:08.606
NOW, LANI. ALL ON THE COVER
OF INSIDE SPORTS.

02:08.737 --> 02:10.826
-BUT HE'S TAKING THEM TO ALASKA.

02:10.955 --> 02:14.612
-I FINALLY CHECKED ON PETER,
HE'S LIVING IN JUNEAU,

02:14.743 --> 02:16.353
ONE OF THE STOPS ON THE CRUISE.

02:16.484 --> 02:18.747
-SO, YOU'RE GOING TO INTRODUCE
ASHLEY TO HER DADDY.

02:18.877 --> 02:20.749
-"CONGRATULATIONS,
YOU'RE THE WINNER

02:20.879 --> 02:23.708
"OF THE PRINCESS CRUISES
ALASKAN AIRLINES SWEEPSTAKES."

02:23.839 --> 02:25.145
I'M GOING TO ALASKA!

02:26.276 --> 02:27.625
-WE'VE GOT THOUSANDS OF STONES

02:27.756 --> 02:29.584
FROM JUST ONE OF THESE EMERALDS.

02:29.714 --> 02:31.803
WE RISKED OUR LIVES
DIVING FOR THESE.

02:31.934 --> 02:33.631
-WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

02:33.762 --> 02:35.503
-I'M TALKING ABOUT GETTING
OUR FAIR SHARE OF THE PROFITS.

02:35.633 --> 02:36.939
-ARE YOU FORGETTING WHO
WE'RE DEALING WITH, HERE?

02:37.069 --> 02:38.288
LOOK, THESE GUYS ARE KILLERS.

02:38.419 --> 02:39.768
THEY'D KILL TO GET
THESE EMERALDS.

02:39.898 --> 02:40.725
THEY'LL KILL TO KEEP THEM.

02:50.518 --> 02:52.476
-I DON'T KNOW, BUT I THINK
WE'VE BEEN DOUBLE-CROSSED.

02:53.085 --> 02:54.565
-REMEMBER WHAT SHE LOOKS LIKE?

02:54.696 --> 02:56.654
BLOND HAIR, BLUE EYES,
THE PERFECT GIRL NEXT DOOR.

02:56.785 --> 02:59.091
-I'M CLAIR HODGES, NOW.
I'M A REDHEAD.

02:59.831 --> 03:01.224
WE MAY HAVE A PROBLEM HERE.

03:01.355 --> 03:03.487
QUINN'S BODY HAS
FLOATED TO THE SURFACE.

03:03.618 --> 03:04.706
-STOP THE BOAT!

03:06.664 --> 03:08.666
-LESLIE: THE LIFEGUARDS
HAVE ALREADY SPOTTED IT.

03:09.972 --> 03:11.103
COULDN'T TELL IF
HE'S DEAD OR ALIVE.

03:22.071 --> 03:22.854
-ARE YOU OKAY?

03:22.985 --> 03:24.334
-I'M NOT SURE.

03:24.465 --> 03:26.118
-CODY: SO ARE YOU
GUYS GOING OUT, OR WHAT?

03:26.249 --> 03:27.598
-HOBIE: ACTUALLY, I'M
GONNA TAKE HER ON THE CRUISE.

03:27.729 --> 03:29.339
-MITCH: YOU'RE GONNA
TAKE A GIRL YOU JUST MET

03:29.470 --> 03:31.559
ON AN 8-DAY ALASKAN CRUISE?

03:31.689 --> 03:33.735
-SHE'S A NICE GIRL,
I WANT TO HELP HER OUT.

03:33.865 --> 03:36.433
-YOU SHOULD'VE LISTENED TO ME,
YOU BASTARD.

03:36.564 --> 03:37.739
GREED IS GOOD.

03:37.869 --> 03:39.044
BYE-BYE, BABY.

03:39.741 --> 03:41.395
-LISTEN, I WANT
THOSE EMERALDS BACK.

03:41.525 --> 03:44.093
I DON'T EVER WANT TO SEE
MISS LESLIE STRYKER AGAIN, EVER.

03:44.224 --> 03:45.703
-I GUARANTEE YOU
SHE'LL NEVER GET OFF

03:45.834 --> 03:47.444
THAT CRUISE SHIP ALIVE.

03:49.925 --> 03:51.405
-GAVIN IS ON THE SHIP.

03:51.535 --> 03:54.146
I PROMISE YOU,
HE WILL NOT FIND THE EMERALDS.

03:55.104 --> 03:56.627
-HAVE A NICE DINNER.
-AREN'T YOU GONNA JOIN US?

03:56.758 --> 04:00.065
-NO, THAT'S OKAY. WE KNOW
WHEN WE'RE NOT WANTED.

04:00.892 --> 04:03.025
-WELL, WHAT'S THE WORST
THAT COULD HAPPEN, HUH?

04:03.808 --> 04:05.941
PETER WANTS NOTHING TO DO
WITH YOU AND ASHLEY,

04:06.071 --> 04:08.204
THEN COME BACK HOME.

04:09.597 --> 04:12.252
-LET'S STOP TALKING.
LET'S JUST DANCE.

04:13.688 --> 04:15.037
I GUESS THIS IS A
MOMENT OF TRUTH,

04:15.777 --> 04:17.168
I JUST HOPE I'M DOING
THE RIGHT THING.

04:17.300 --> 04:18.345
COME HERE, SWEETIE.

04:18.910 --> 04:20.476
LET'S FEED YOU BEFORE
YOU MEET YOUR DADDY.

04:20.608 --> 04:22.784
-I JUST HOPE PETER
LIKES SURPRISES.

04:22.914 --> 04:25.003
-LESLIE: STOP TELLING ME
TO CALM DOWN, HE'S FOUND ME.

04:25.134 --> 04:26.918
I DON'T HAVE TIME TO EXPLAIN.

04:27.049 --> 04:28.572
-MITCH: HOW ABOUT
A CLAIR HODGES.

04:28.703 --> 04:31.401
-THAT ROOM'S OCCUPIED
BY A MISS LESLIE STRYKER.

04:31.532 --> 04:34.361
-MITCH: LESLIE STRYKER?
WHAT THE HELL'S GOING ON?

04:34.491 --> 04:36.276
CLAIR, HOLD IT! WAIT
A MINUTE, CLAIR!

04:36.406 --> 04:38.190
STOP! WHO IS THIS GUY?

04:43.108 --> 04:45.546
-LESLIE: HE DOESN'T HAVE
THE EMERALDS, I DO.

04:46.808 --> 04:48.418
I DON'T HAVE TIME TO EXPLAIN.

04:48.549 --> 04:50.725
JUST MEET ME IN A TOWN
CALLED CICELY.

04:51.421 --> 04:53.902
IT'S DUE EAST OF
MENDENHALL GLACIER.

04:55.120 --> 04:56.687
DON'T WORRY ABOUT HOW
I'M GONNA GET THERE,

04:56.818 --> 04:57.775
JUST BE THERE.

