36:25.095 --> 36:29.491
-MITCH AND NEELY, THE TWO
OF YOU ARE UNITED TODAY

36:29.622 --> 36:31.493
AS MORE THAN JUST A COUPLE.

36:32.059 --> 36:35.497
YOU ARE, ALONG WITH
HOBIE AND ASHLEY,

36:36.063 --> 36:39.066
ALSO UNITED AS A FAMILY.

36:39.849 --> 36:42.330
THEREFORE, WITH THE
POWER VESTED IN ME,

36:42.896 --> 36:45.420
AS CAPTAIN OF THE DAWN PRINCESS.

36:45.986 --> 36:47.466
IT IS WITH GREAT HONOR

36:47.596 --> 36:50.382
THAT I PRONOUNCE YOU
HUSBAND AND WIFE.

36:52.340 --> 36:53.472
YOU MAY KISS THE BRIDE.

37:07.442 --> 37:08.748
-I LOVE YOU.

37:09.401 --> 37:11.011
-LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,

37:11.141 --> 37:15.407
I PRESENT MR. AND MRS.
MITCH BUCHANNON AND FAMILY.

37:26.592 --> 37:28.071
-CODY: CONGRATULATIONS, BROTHER.

37:30.726 --> 37:32.380
-OH YEAH, YOU'RE DARN TOOTIN'.

37:34.687 --> 37:35.557
-I SMELL TROUBLE.

37:36.645 --> 37:38.168
-PERFECT JOB FOR THE NEW DAD.

37:38.778 --> 37:42.172
-WE'LL BE RIGHT BACK,
WE GOTTA CHANGE A DIAPER.

37:44.436 --> 37:45.263
-THANK YOU!

